The paper proposes a hybrid precoding scheme for millimeter wave massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The focus on energy efficiency suggests a possible fit with systems and control (cs.SY). The use of antenna mappings and RF chains suggests a possible fit with multimedia (cs.MM) and architecture (cs.AR).
